extendScope

public void extendScope(IDesign neighbor)
Description copied from interface: IDesign
Extends the scope for parameter access to all parameters of the neighbor design. Addressing is done absolute with respect to the parameter names, which has as a consequence that parameters in neighboring designs may not share the same id.
